snippet.title: Black Forest - Official 1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Black Forest is a base-building survival strategy game developed by Lemuria. Players embody the chief of an unlucky village full of danger, death, and despair. The ultimate goal is to gather resources, prepare the village as best you can, and survive the night. Black Forest is available now in full 1.0 launch on PC.
